创造人民，把他们从群眠变为人民。布尔什维克回答社会革命党人说；人民创造英雄。这本书是在为社会革命党人张目。一切这样的书都将为社会单命党人张目，都将危害我们整个布尔什维克的事业","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"ebbc266320","type":"paragraph","text":"建议把这本书烧掉","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"e30e3a4781","type":"paragraph","text":"约·斯大林译自1953年11月《历史问题","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"ecc8908ad7","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集第11期第21页","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"642bc1633d","type":"paragraph","text":"第14卷第185页","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"18331e5c53","type":"paragraph","text":"1）这是斯大林给苏联列宁共产主义青年团中央委员会儿童读物出版社的一封信。一一编者注","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"38cbfce35d","type":"paragraph","text":"诸夏怀斯社","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"f9db4a0fd8","type":"paragraph","text":"二O一七年五月制作","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"cd60bef39e","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林选集","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"4dbfd788d3","type":"paragraph","text":"第四卷","index":14,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"cbaabe4634","type":"paragraph","text":"全世界无蓬者，联合起求！","index":15,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"69e924ca26","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林选集","index":16,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":"865578ff37","type":"paragraph","text":"第四卷","index":17,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"88dac5c6fd"},{"id":